author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Banque Cantonale du Valais: FY Net Profit Up At CHF 64.0 Mln
text:
March 7 (Reuters) - Banque Cantonale du Valais:
* FY NET INTEREST INCOME UP AT CHF 162.6 MILLION * FY NET FEE AND COMMISSION INCOME UP BY 13.8 PERCENT AT CHF 39.4 MILLION
* FY OPERATING INCOME UP BY 12.2 PERCENT AT CHF 112.6 MILLION
* PROPOSED DIVIDEND OF CHF 3.15 PER SHARE * OUTLOOK 2018: SEES BUSINESS RESULTS TO BE AT THE SAME LEVEL AS IN PREVIOUS YEARS
* IN 2018 SHOULD REACH ANNUAL RESULT THAT WILL MATCH THE GOOD BALANCE OF 2017
